Think on this:  what is up with &quot;No-drop&quot; gear?  I mean, take some ultimate uber weapon that is granted by a demi-god through a quest and it enters your hand and &quot;binds to your soul&quot; or some shit.  Ok.  Plausible.  Could make for some interesting dynamics or for cursed items...<br>
