<br>
Instead, why not tone down the items?  I mean, why is it steel was soooo obsolete?  In my opinion, EQ finally made tradeskills viable.  Those that worked hard at them could create some awesome items as I think it should be.  Sure, there should be potent magic out there to be won, epics to be earned, artifacts to uncover... but, to make these items so available and necessarry for &quot;End-game&quot; play...<br>
