<br>
OR, randomize the whole freaking thing in a way that, you may get an alternate item (of nothing but sale value to vendors), or you might get the 25FR/CR gear, OR you might get an item of lesser resistance score than that.  Make it a unique item so you can only have one... attatch code that does not allow you to get more than one in a period of XX hours RL time...<br>
<br>
There are a number of ways to lessen, curb, and eliminate twinking blahblahblah... but, will the people spend gobs of cash each month to pay for it?<br>
